{"tid":1987923,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"睇左咁多異世界動漫，終於搵到我認為最好睇的番","createTime":"2020-04-24T22:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T01:16:02.000Z","uid":124372,"like":8,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"20e0ae2cf76b072a28950c239905bed293cbb606","tid":1987923,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T22:06:18.000Z","msg":"re:從零開始的異世界生活<br />\n其實條橋好簡單<br />\n大家都有個打過機罷<br />\n每次打大佬前都會去save point<br />\n萬一打輸了可以由save point再打<br />\n直到打贏為止<br />\n男主就係有大技死亡回歸<br />\n每次打輸了都獲得經驗糾正錯誤再打<br />\n雖說得簡單但故事卻非常複習<br />\n當中亦隱藏好多迷<br />\n另外人設亦好各有特色<br />\n雖然不算後宮番但有半精靈皇後選人愛蜜莉雅、各女僕雷姆<br />\n壞人亦極度變態<br />\n印象最深係獵腸者、魔女教大祭師<br />\n以下都係我鐘意的角色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkfqtfX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkfqtfX.jpg&h=0572e346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愛蜜莉雅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOdvEox.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOdvEox.jpg&h=cf078b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雷姆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ChDOgY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ChDOgY.jpg&h=2f994b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獵腸者<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GPPuUXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGPPuUXg.jpg&h=87d77de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n魔女教 大祭師<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ni2z54t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNi2z54t.jpg&h=6778233b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f98812683d6e092877cba014b219959a9c69c26","tid":1987923,"uid":213607,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T22:11:38.000Z","msg":"個post開遲左幾多年"},{"pid":"e220ad016a08b3be3d704c8ca5c58574f39e1433","tid":1987923,"uid":263150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f98812683d6e092877cba014b219959a9c69c26","tid":1987923,"uid":213607,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T22:11:38.000Z","msg":